---
title: Creamy Mozzarella Rigatoni with courgette ribbons and fresh parsley
description: In this recipe, courgette is turned into delicate ribbons and baked with a rich, creamy tomato sauce and globs of melting mozzarella. This is a pasta dish with a twist, and one you're sure to enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W48_IE_IEXFVCLV0013-3_Main__3high-329d9fdd.jpg
